:

*Vrstu* jabuka je lako prepoznati po karakterističnom obliku. (It is easy to recognize the type of apple by its characteristic shape.)

*Vrsta* povrća koju volim je tikvica. (The type of vegetable I like is pumpkin.)

*Vrste* ptica se mogu videti na obali reke. (Different kinds of birds can be seen on the banks of the river.)

*Vrstom* ribe se bavi moj otac. (My father is dealing with the type of fish.)

*Vrstu* drveta za izradu namještaja je lako odabrati. (It is easy to choose the kind of wood for the furniture production.)